title: Mass Effect is Back! - Kinda Funny Games Daily 11.09.20
description:
Blessing and Tim kick off the week by talking about the return of Mass Effect, reviews for Bugsnax and Assassin's Creed Valhalla, and more.

Time Stamps - 
00:00:00 - Start-
00:04:00 - Housekeeping
Two reviews just dropped over on Youtube.com/KindaFunnyGames, Bugsnax and Assassin’s Creed Valhalla
Thank you to our Patreon Producers:Tom Bock & Black Jack
The Roper Report   -
00:06:25 - Mass Effect is BACK - Casey Hudson @ Bioware
00:17:20 - Everybody’s talking about Bugnsnax! - Review roundup
00:24:35 - Assassin’s Creed Valhalla review roundup
00:29:11 - There’s a new PS5 launch trailer with some interesting tidbits
00:33:15 - Speaking of PS5, a future Update Will Allow Output 8K Resolutions - Adam Bankhurst @ IGN
00:40:34 - Take-Two is in talks to buy Codemasters - Brendain Sinclair @ GiBIz
00:42:40 - Out today
00:45:00 -  Ad  
00:52:40 - When do you think we'll see our first next gen 10/10 game? - Best Friends Q:Nick
00:58:00 -  Do you think there are too many trailers especially when it comes to shorter 10 hour story experiences? - Best Friends Q:Super
01:00:40 - You‘re Wrong
Tomorrow’s Hosts:Blessing and Imran
